	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>Febr&#39;y 21<hi rend="sup">st</hi> 1855</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
				<p><add>Hebrew</add></p>
				<p><persName role="author">Michael Light</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>187 Forsyth <sic>street</sic></placeName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>February 21&#44; 1855</date></p>
				<p>Honored friend&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Dr. Simon Abrahams</persName> told me that <persName>Mr. Norr</persName> has been temporari&#45;<lb/>ly elected steward of the hospital&#44; and I therefore assume that <persName>Mr. Norr</persName><lb/> is disposed to accept this and that he will gladly take the post.  I<lb/> have therefore declined to apply for the position of teacher at the<lb/> Hebrew Education Society and permit myself to ask you&#44; in case you can<lb/> be of help to me in the attainment of a position of the said society<lb/> in <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44; to do so.  For I am without a livelihood&#44; &#8220;May God<lb/> reward you doubly in return&#8221;.  In my letter to <persName>Mr. Binswanger</persName>&#44; I re&#45;<lb/>ferred to you&#44; and I ask you&#44; in any event&#44; to reply to this letter&#44; and<lb/> to be good enough to let me know whether the teacher up till now will<lb/> remain or not&#44; and how high the salary is&#44; whether it is equal for<lb/> both teachers&#44; etc.&#44; If there is no good prospect&#44; I shall decide to<lb/> do something else.  Herewith you receive also the enclosed card which<lb/> I have prepared without completing it for <persName>Mr. N. Oettinger</persName>&#44; since he ex&#45;<lb/>plained to me that he himself hopes to sell the prayer books.</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">With <sic>th</sic> wish that this letter may find you in the best of<lb/> health&#44; I sign with all respect&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">Devotedly&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">Michael Light</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(11)"><placeName>187 Forsythe Street</placeName></p>
		</body>
